comments: Readings were really interesting, as were Dr. Nock\'s lectures. He is witty which is a plus. He\'s critical of the field of clinical psychology and psychological treatment research while still conveying hope of folks working for positive change. Great class. Learned a lot and got some great new perspective without an unreasonable amount of stress.
